<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>纽约时报 &amp;gt; 美国 &amp;gt; 政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/on-politics</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 14:57:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>民主党人曾经痛恨不公正地划分选区。现在他们正在努力争取。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/20/us/politics/virginia-gerrymandering-referendum.html</link><description>该党在弗吉尼亚州寻求额外的优势之际，该党在绘制政治地图上的党派思维发生了变化——领导人表示，这在很大程度上是因为特朗普总统的策略。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 21:26:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/20/us/politics/virginia-gerrymandering-referendum.html</guid></item><item><title>缅因州选民在 2026 年参议院选举前的想法</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/17/us/politics/maine-senate-election-collins-platner-mills.html</link><description>该州的读者向我们讲述了该州高风险的参议院竞选。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/17/us/politics/maine-senate-election-collins-platner-mills.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普和共和党能否收回有关经济的信息？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/15/us/politics/trump-taxes-economy-iran-war.html</link><description>今天是纳税日，但该国的大部分注意力都集中在一场不受欢迎的战争上。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 21:31:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/15/us/politics/trump-taxes-economy-iran-war.html</guid></item><item><title>埃里克·斯瓦尔韦尔下台后，加州州长竞选会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/13/us/politics/swalwell-california-governor.html</link><description>对于民主党人来说，这出戏的影响远远超出了州内范围。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 22:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/13/us/politics/swalwell-california-governor.html</guid></item><item><title>2028 年民主党可能的候选人已经在争取黑人选民的支持</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/10/us/politics/black-voters-democrats-2028.html</link><description>可能的总统候选人已经在争取重要的民主党选区。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 21:32:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/10/us/politics/black-voters-democrats-2028.html</guid></item><item><title>谁为 2026 年中期选举提供资金？很多钱都无法追踪。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/midterms-elections-funding-pac.html</link><description>流入政治体系的大量资金最终无法追踪。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 22:21:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/midterms-elections-funding-pac.html</guid></item><item><title>佛罗里达州的选区重划战争、佐治亚州的决选和最新的政治新闻</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/redistricting-virginia-florida-ga-special-election-republicans.html</link><description>随着未来两周最后期限的临近，两者都没有完全按照党派计划进行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 21:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/redistricting-virginia-florida-ga-special-election-republicans.html</guid></item><item><title>随着民主党在中期选举前变得乐观，六场参议院竞选值得关注</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/03/us/politics/senate-races-midterms-primary-election.html</link><description>对于该党来说，夺回控制权仍然是一项艰巨的任务。这是最新的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 15:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/03/us/politics/senate-races-midterms-primary-election.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普支持的路易斯安那州初选候选人也赞扬了 DEI。会伤害她吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/01/us/politics/julia-letlow-louisiana-republican-primary.html</link><description>路易斯安那州众议员朱莉娅·莱特洛 (Julia Letlow) 竞选参议员比尔·卡西迪 (Bill Cassidy)，但她因 2020 年的言论而面临保守派的反击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 21:39:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/01/us/politics/julia-letlow-louisiana-republican-primary.html</guid></item><item><title>缅因州、密歇根州及其他地区初选速成班</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/primary-elections-maine-michigan.html</link><description>这是关于接下来要发生的事情的速成课程。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 23:41:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/30/us/politics/primary-elections-maine-michigan.html</guid></item></channel></rss>